{"kind":"symbol","metadata":{"role":"symbol","symbolKind":"property","modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"progress"}],"roleHeading":"Instance Property","title":"progress","externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNOfflinePack(py)progress","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"progress"}]},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePack\/progress"},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The pack’s current progress."}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnofflinepack\/progress"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["occ"],"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"@property"},{"kind":"text","text":" ("},{"kind":"keyword","text":"nonatomic"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"readonly"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePackProgress","preciseIdentifier":"c:@S@MLNOfflinePackProgress","text":"MLNOfflinePackProgress"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"progress"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion","type":"heading","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The progress of an inactive or completed pack is computed lazily, and all its"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"fields are set to 0 by default. To request the pack’s progress, use the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"-requestProgress"},{"type":"text","text":" method. To get notified when the progress becomes"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"known and when it changes, observe KVO change notifications on this pack’s"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"state"},{"type":"text","text":" key path. Alternatively, you can add an observer for"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePackProgressChangedNotification","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":"s about this pack that come from the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"default notification center."}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"sections":[],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePack"]]},"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNOfflinePackProgress":{"role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"MLNOfflinePackProgress","kind":"identifier"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnofflinepackprogress","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"A structure containing information about an offline pack’s current download","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"progress.","type":"text"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePackProgress","type":"topic","title":"MLNOfflinePackProgress"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNOfflineStorage":{"fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNOfflineStorage"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"MLNOfflineStorage implements a singleton (shared object) that manages offline"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"packs and ambient caching. All of this class’s instance methods are asynchronous,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"reflecting the fact that offline resources are stored in a database. The shared"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"object maintains a canonical collection of offline packs in its "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"packs"},{"type":"text","text":" property."}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnofflinestorage","type":"topic","kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","title":"MLNOfflineStorage","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProjec